  "title": "chore(beta): cannot release beta",
  "body": "Since jsDelivr do not care about dist-tags like the @beta tag we were\nusing on npm:\njsdelivr/jsdelivr#8841 (comment)\n\nWe cannot provide a release-beta script because then we cannot release\nany patch fixes while working on a beta.\n\nAt some point if npmcdn.com gains traction, it might be a better\nchoice for us: https://npmcdn.com/\n",
